Ned Luke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ned_Luke 0 Ned Luke is an American actor. He is known for voicing and acting as Michael De Santa in the 2013 video game Grand Theft Auto V and Raffles in the animated movie Rover Dangerfield. He has appeared in 29 movies and television shows to date. Ned_Luke is an_American_actor .
